OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA chilly start will lead to a
OL,6,Ffine and dry day today, with plenty of
OL,7,Fsunshine, although the sunshine may
OL,8,Fturn hazy at times. Feeling warm for
OL,9,Fmost, although a little fresher near
OL,10,Fthe south coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA fine evening with some late
OL,13,Fsunshine. Overnight will remain dry
OL,14,Fwith further clear spells. A little
OL,15,Fchilly in the countryside but not as
OL,16,Fcold as recent nights.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
