OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FAnother fine and dry day
OL,6,Fwith spells of sunshine for much of
OL,7,Fthe region. Possibly turning cloudier
OL,8,Fat times across Cornwall, especially
OL,9,Fduring the afternoon. Feeling warm
OL,10,Fwith light winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,13,FCooler and more changeable on
OL,14,FThursday, with spells of rain and
OL,15,Fshowers. Likely to stay unsettled on
OL,16,FFriday and Saturday with further rain
OL,17,Fat times, and temperatures nearer to
OL,18,Faverage.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
